{"tid":1762554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動討論】我地需要一個死線共識，不如12月9日？","createTime":"2019-11-29T16:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T15:00:01.000Z","uid":310242,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9173e7a19e5b6164bbac5d2ebac4e0102c5a0c33","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:20:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對唔住小弟仲係P牌仔但睇左文先</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">小弟<span style=\"font-size: small;\">文</span>長，對唔住咁多位</span><br />\n是咁的，經歷過11月24日投票後，連登陸續出現不同嘅風向，小弟是藉第一次貼文想大家諗諗少少野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.社會暫時回復「平靜」，採取行動前需要一個預告，並將責任歸咎政府身上</span></span><br />\n<br />\n相信大家最近睇連登一定好攰，因為大家因應唔同定位而產生唔同睇法<br />\n<br />\n真勇武手足傷亡嚴重，的確需要休息//<br />\n中前排開花手足會好上心，「全部行動冇曬，唔可以降溫啊」//<br />\n可能亦都有手足主張要俾和理非出返黎遊行下//<br />\n你亂咁叫手足出黎行動推佢地死啫//<br />\n<br />\n就混亂見解當中，我建議共識的死線定係以下大型活動後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HziVsVZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHziVsVZ.jpg&h=5ad5ef2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REsfsV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREsfsV5.jpg&h=09d7cd51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得最初嘅戰術 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理 &gt; 死線 &gt; 勇武</span><br />\n<br />\n1.即使遊行未必成功搞到，但希望大家有一個心理準備，會係未來邊一個「明確日子」再次行動升級<br />\n<br />\n2.主動出擊，成為掌握輿論嘅主導者，明確連藍絲都知道「係政府錯過最後機會，令香港再混亂」<br />\n<br />\n3.連登日日互屌睇得多好撚攰，不如趁有一個比較明確嘅日子，做一個共識出黎，等大家唔洗再互屌，唔洗再諗邊個係「五毛」邊個係「分化撚」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.切勿輕視敵人，社會係偽和平但極權係勁左</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我明白，咁攰大家可能要笑下放鬆下，笑尻啊何已完等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但切勿輕敵</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nDjEUFf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnDjEUFf.jpg&h=ee873a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和平行動都已經拎步槍，其實係好嚴重好危險</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1LQgT3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1LQgT3.jpg&h=87410e60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如圖，對家嘅行動一直冇停過，甚至誇張到你大叫「光復香港」都有一隊狗出現附近</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因此，班狗禮貌左？唔一定係區選輸左死曬狗<br />\n因此，班狗禮貌左？唔一定係驚人權法死全家<br />\n<br />\n反而，鄧小強上任配合區選降溫，藉此做下公關慢慢搞散<br />\n<br />\n我係一個一直都好關注政治嘅人，我好清楚<br />\n今場運動咁多人走出黎絕對唔係因為政治責任，而係一次又一次警暴令更多人走出黎<br />\n<br />\n當你只笑尻佢尻縮嘅時候，其實都反映左好大危機下...<br />\n一個打仗嘅士兵從來唔會睇低，取笑敵人，而係腦袋冷靜分析，身體勇武<br />\n<br />\n//當善忘香港人忘記義士的鮮血，因少許甜頭而加以冷嘲熱諷，最後再沒有更過份警暴出現的時候，已經麻木的人群再不會走出來，再沒有機會及能力走出來//<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.唔需要死線，每日都可以做嘅任務</span></span><br />\n<br />\n//<span style=\"font-size: large;\">文宣繼續做，一係全部黃街坊一齊貼，一係小隊靜靜地貼</span><br />\n<br />\n返公司學校印幾張，隨身帶，見到連儂牆嘅咪順手囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//<span style=\"font-size: large;\">黃色經濟圈，唔止食店所有消費都係黃店內消費</span><br />\n<br />\n和理eat<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.woleieat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.woleieat&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=c355e98c\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.woleieat</a><br />\nWhatsGap<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gotcha.hk.map\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.gotcha.hk.map&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=c69bfa9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gotcha.hk.map</a><br />\n<br />\n其實有待手足發現<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後重申一次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家覺得死線共識如何</span>，歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時候革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">支爆啦唔該</span>"},{"pid":"1a7a3167fc1e2c7ca14b9e031bb8e7e4220a48e8","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"092c0ac0be4d5cc18db4d93107dfd71a56d3fb5b","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"7835369f816514c99f4279678d8688fefc239fbc","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"550b4f018381bdedb57e25cb280455485784e3fa","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"a4cec3cb0969ef0783800e65f0cef06caff66096","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"7d4e630b764b47e1d5a08ed66a80f57644695711","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"2dc1216e54647ddadfdace5d7d6ad431d671975f","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"8b89b4a9d3a97326fd9d4d3e5b7a7bd6a6261475","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"a398f39be82383ca5285c3e2515f053c5661411e","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"403d4fbef6ca406c708782c93404306a75494a77","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"a3fdc3956bbb73541d6ee286f3ea0e69c6d7e5ef","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"10/10 P牌仔自推有冇用架wtf"},{"pid":"58ee1d3801921c3788d01b82c77458a276e866b0","tid":1762554,"uid":235769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:25:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d5a58db87257c2913d718c9b5c8d74823297a6a","tid":1762554,"uid":235769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:25:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e34615b844270b417c190ce636c63b5f420cc62","tid":1762554,"uid":235769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:26:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7900f0a206a2ce1faa5b7e762d469ca4e09f2669","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:28:29.000Z","msg":"就快半年啦，勇武同和理唔再係標籤，唔係label一個人嘅定位<br />\n<br />\n而係形容詞，「今晚感恩節集會，我和理先」//「救手足，拎gear出黎，今晚幾點勇武」"},{"pid":"3706a7e4432af2795540af59066cb5d9d2a38f01","tid":1762554,"uid":306528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:30:10.000Z","msg":"我地需要一個死線共識，不如12月9日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔需要死線，........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwt?????"},{"pid":"77a0a145844b49293591f6084914a002d7723c89","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3706a7e4432af2795540af59066cb5d9d2a38f01","tid":1762554,"uid":306528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:30:10.000Z","msg":"我地需要一個死線共識，不如12月9日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔需要死線，........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwt?????"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:32:53.000Z","msg":"sor，意思應該係「即使唔需要死線但每日都可以做嘅行動」"},{"pid":"9149c687680c9c055b77d67b4806d65dac226862","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:34:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.死線前後都可以做的每日任務</span></span><br />\n<br />\nsor，語癌令大家get錯野<br />\n<br />\n我想表達嘅意思係，既然有冇死線呢樣野都好，大家都可以做以下嘅每日任務"},{"pid":"ceb056f87ba17428cdeb03d9595f6e9351c6bdfe","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"有關第3點黃色經濟圈，可以參考呢一篇文章，入去幫樓主寫低資料<br />\n<br />\n[url]我地要搞既係黃色經濟圈 唔係黃色餐廳圈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738321</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]"},{"pid":"ab9bd812e2b34b6837a4672140d512099c8674fa","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"12.9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e913a91eb2096291698b8bb4efa7a2f39ba4431f","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"12.9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a28775f5f00e171acd327edc5962d13b2f18aa","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"12.9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275e84e3d1c800c21b40820ff1c773baa6b50eb8","tid":1762554,"uid":308032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"Push (P牌冇力推) 請手足幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4ec3de2737e75c8ff2d33dd737b94e302729e7","tid":1762554,"uid":318780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T18:22:08.000Z","msg":"P牌都照推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"9149c687680c9c055b77d67b4806d65dac226862","tid":1762554,"uid":310242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:34:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.死線前後都可以做的每日任務</span></span><br />\n<br />\nsor，語癌令大家get錯野<br />\n<br />\n我想表達嘅意思係，既然有冇死線呢樣野都好，大家都可以做以下嘅每日任務"}}